---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout
  title="About — Nate Cowperthwaite"
  description="Chef, self-taught developer, and co-founder. 10+ years in professional kitchens across Maine and Texas. Building software rooted in real kitchen problems since 2025."
>
  <main id="main-content">

    <!-- ===== HERO ===== -->
    <section class="about-hero hero-gradient-bg">
      <div class="orb-container" aria-hidden="true">
        <div class="orb orb-blue"></div>
        <div class="orb orb-indigo"></div>
      </div>
      <div class="about-hero-inner">
        <div class="animate-fade-in-up">
          <span class="badge badge-blue">
            <svg width="11" height="11" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2.5" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" aria-hidden="true"><path d="M20 21v-2a4 4 0 0 0-4-4H8a4 4 0 0 0-4 4v2"/><circle cx="12" cy="7" r="4"/></svg>
            About Me
          </span>
        </div>
        <h1 class="about-hero-title animate-fade-in-up" style="animation-delay:0.07s">
          Chef by trade.<br />
          <span class="shimmer-text">Builder by necessity.</span>
        </h1>
        <p class="about-hero-sub animate-fade-in-up" style="animation-delay:0.14s">
          I've spent 12+ years in professional kitchens across Maine and Texas — working the line,
          leading BOH teams, co-founding a food concept, and running operations from scratch every
          single day. In 2025 I started building software to fix the problems no existing tool
          bothered to solve. That side project got serious fast.
        </p>
        <p class="about-hero-back animate-fade-in-up" style="animation-delay:0.20s">
          <a href="/dev" class="inline-link">&larr; Back to Dev Home</a>
        </p>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- ===== WHO I AM ===== -->
    <section class="section section-blue-tint">
      <h2 class="section-heading reveal">Who I Am</h2>
      <p class="section-sub reveal">The honest version.</p>

      <div class="who-grid stagger">

        <div class="who-card card card-blue-left reveal">
          <div class="who-card-icon" aria-hidden="true">
            <svg width="28" height="28" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.8" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="M14.7 6.3a1 1 0 0 0 0 1.4l1.6 1.6a1 1 0 0 0 1.4 0l3.77-3.77a6 6 0 0 1-7.94 7.94l-6.91 6.91a2.12 2.12 0 0 1-3-3l6.91-6.91a6 6 0 0 1 7.94-7.94l-3.76 3.76z"/></svg>
          </div>
          <h3 class="who-card-title">Still a Working Chef</h3>
          <p class="who-card-text">
            Kitchen work is still my day job — currently Shift Manager at Seasons in Bangor, ME.
            I've worked every level of BOH from prep cook and dishwasher to sous chef and lead cook
            across a dozen kitchens in Maine and Texas. Cooking isn't a backstory; it's the whole point.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div class="who-card card card-blue-left reveal">
          <div class="who-card-icon" aria-hidden="true">
            <svg width="28" height="28" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.8" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><polyline points="16 18 22 12 16 6"/><polyline points="8 6 2 12 8 18"/></svg>
          </div>
          <h3 class="who-card-title">Self-Taught Developer</h3>
          <p class="who-card-text">
            No bootcamp. No CS degree. I started coding in 2025 using agentic workflows, AI APIs,
            and a lot of trial-and-error. Every gap in my knowledge got filled by a real problem
            that demanded a solution — recipe tooling, kitchen ops automation, AI-assisted workflows.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div class="who-card card card-blue-left reveal">
          <div class="who-card-icon" aria-hidden="true">
            <svg width="28" height="28" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.8" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="M17 21v-2a4 4 0 0 0-4-4H5a4 4 0 0 0-4 4v2"/><circle cx="9" cy="7" r="4"/><path d="M23 21v-2a4 4 0 0 0-3-3.87"/><path d="M16 3.13a4 4 0 0 1 0 7.75"/></svg>
          </div>
          <h3 class="who-card-title">Co-Founder</h3>
          <p class="who-card-text">
            Co-founded Northern Fixin's / Half Baked Co. — a Maine-inspired elevated café,
            scratch bakehouse, and food truck concept. Brick-and-mortar café targeting 2027.
            The business is what originally drove me to build software; nothing off the shelf
            fit what we actually needed.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div class="who-card card card-blue-left reveal">
          <div class="who-card-icon" aria-hidden="true">
            <svg width="28" height="28" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.8" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="M12 2a4 4 0 0 1 4 4v1h1a3 3 0 0 1 0 6h-1v1a4 4 0 0 1-8 0v-1H7a3 3 0 0 1 0-6h1V6a4 4 0 0 1 4-4Z"/><circle cx="12" cy="10" r="2"/></svg>
          </div>
          <h3 class="who-card-title">Problem-First Mindset</h3>
          <p class="who-card-text">
            Nothing I build starts from "what's a cool tech stack." It starts from a specific,
            repeating friction point — something slow, something missing, something that
            should already exist. Irritation is a better motivator than inspiration.
          </p>
        </div>

      </div>
    </section>

    <div class="divider-animated"></div>

    <!-- ===== WORK HISTORY ===== -->
    <section class="section section-blue-wash">
      <h2 class="section-heading reveal">Work History</h2>
      <p class="section-sub reveal">12 years of kitchens, a few detours, and one pivot that stuck.</p>

      <div class="history-cols">

        <!-- CULINARY -->
        <div class="history-group reveal">
          <div class="history-group-header">
            <span class="history-icon" aria-hidden="true">
              <svg width="15" height="15" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2.2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="M6 2v6a6 6 0 0 0 12 0V2"/><line x1="12" y1="14" x2="12" y2="22"/></svg>
            </span>
            <span class="history-group-label">Culinary</span>
          </div>
          <div class="history-list">

            <div class="history-item">
              <div class="history-meta">
                <span class="history-role">Shift Manager</span>
                <span class="history-date">Mar 2025 – Present</span>
              </div>
              <div class="history-place">Seasons &mdash; Bangor, ME</div>
            </div>

            <div class="history-item">
              <div class="history-meta">
                <span class="history-role">Bar &amp; Kitchen</span>
                <span class="history-date">Jul 2024 – Mar 2025</span>
              </div>
              <div class="history-place">Mason's Brewing Company &mdash; Brewer, ME</div>
            </div>

            <div class="history-item">
              <div class="history-meta">
                <span class="history-role">Cook</span>
                <span class="history-date">Oct 2023 – Mar 2024</span>
              </div>
              <div class="history-place">Harvest Moon Delis &mdash; Brewer, ME</div>
            </div>

            <div class="history-item">
              <div class="history-meta">
                <span class="history-role">Cook</span>
                <span class="history-date">May – Jul 2023</span>
              </div>
              <div class="history-place">Water's Edge Restaurant &amp; Bar &mdash; Edgecomb, ME</div>
            </div>

            <div class="history-item history-item-highlight">
              <div class="history-meta">
                <span class="history-role">Chef / Line Cook</span>
                <span class="history-date">Mar – May 2022</span>
              </div>
              <div class="history-place">Daddy B's Kitchen &mdash; North Richland Hills, TX</div>
              <div class="history-note">Food truck — direct spark for Northern Fixin's</div>
            </div>

            <div class="history-item">
              <div class="history-meta">
                <span class="history-role">Line Cook</span>
                <span class="history-date">Dec 2021 – Jul 2022</span>
              </div>
              <div class="history-place">Red Ash &mdash; Austin, TX</div>
            </div>

            <div class="history-item">
              <div class="history-meta">
                <span class="history-role">Lead Cook</span>
                <span class="history-date">Feb – May 2022</span>
              </div>
              <div class="history-place">Toasted Coffee + Kitchen &mdash; Fort Worth, TX</div>
            </div>

            <div class="history-item">
              <div class="history-meta">
                <span class="history-role">Chef / Sous Chef</span>
                <span class="history-date">Aug 2020 – Apr 2021</span>
              </div>
              <div class="history-place">Ports of Italy &mdash; Rockport, ME</div>
            </div>

            <div class="history-item">
              <div class="history-meta">
                <span class="history-role">Breakfast Cook</span>
                <span class="history-date">May – Aug 2019</span>
              </div>
              <div class="history-place">Boynton McKay Food Co &mdash; Camden, ME</div>
            </div>

            <div class="history-item">
              <div class="history-meta">
                <span class="history-role">Prep Cook</span>
                <span class="history-date">Nov 2015 – Jun 2016</span>
              </div>
              <div class="history-place">North Italia &mdash; Austin, TX</div>
            </div>

            <div class="history-item history-item-highlight">
              <div class="history-meta">
                <span class="history-role">Chef / Line Cook</span>
                <span class="history-date">May 2014 – Aug 2015</span>
              </div>
              <div class="history-place">Samoset Resort &mdash; Rockport, ME</div>
              <div class="history-note">Where it started</div>
            </div>

          </div>
        </div>

        <!-- DEV + OTHER -->
        <div class="history-right">

          <div class="history-group reveal">
            <div class="history-group-header">
              <span class="history-icon" aria-hidden="true">
                <svg width="15" height="15" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2.2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><polyline points="16 18 22 12 16 6"/><polyline points="8 6 2 12 8 18"/></svg>
              </span>
              <span class="history-group-label">Dev</span>
            </div>
            <div class="history-list">

              <div class="history-item history-item-highlight">
                <div class="history-meta">
                  <span class="history-role">Co-Founder &amp; Developer</span>
                  <span class="history-date">2023 – Present</span>
                </div>
                <div class="history-place">Northern Fixin's / Half Baked Co.</div>
                <div class="history-note">Maine-inspired café &amp; food truck concept. Brick-and-mortar 2027.</div>
              </div>

              <div class="history-item">
                <div class="history-meta">
                  <span class="history-role">Self-Taught Developer</span>
                  <span class="history-date">2025 – Present</span>
                </div>
                <div class="history-place">Independent &mdash; Bangor, ME</div>
                <div class="history-note">CulinaryOS, KitchenKit, CulinaryOps &amp; more</div>
              </div>

            </div>
          </div>

          <div class="history-group reveal" style="margin-top:1.5rem">
            <div class="history-group-header">
              <span class="history-icon" aria-hidden="true">
                <svg width="15" height="15" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2.2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><rect x="2" y="7" width="20" height="14" rx="2"/><path d="M16 7V5a2 2 0 0 0-4 0v2"/><path d="M8 7V5a2 2 0 0 0-4 0v2"/></svg>
              </span>
              <span class="history-group-label">Other</span>
            </div>
            <div class="history-list">

              <div class="history-item">
                <div class="history-meta">
                  <span class="history-role">Tech Supervisor</span>
                  <span class="history-date">Jul 2017 – Sep 2018</span>
                </div>
                <div class="history-place">Staples &mdash; Rockland, ME</div>
              </div>

              <div class="history-item">
                <div class="history-meta">
                  <span class="history-role">Produce Manager</span>
                  <span class="history-date">Jul 2018 – Mar 2019</span>
                </div>
                <div class="history-place">Shaw's Supermarket &mdash; Rockland, ME</div>
              </div>

              <div class="history-item">
                <div class="history-meta">
                  <span class="history-role">Lead Sales Rep</span>
                  <span class="history-date">Jul – Oct 2022</span>
                </div>
                <div class="history-place">MetroPCS &mdash; Augusta, ME</div>
              </div>

            </div>
          </div>

          <div class="history-group reveal" style="margin-top:1.5rem">
            <div class="history-group-header">
              <span class="history-icon" aria-hidden="true">
                <svg width="15" height="15" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2.2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="M22 10v6M2 10l10-5 10 5-10 5z"/><path d="M6 12v5c0 2 2 3 6 3s6-1 6-3v-5"/></svg>
              </span>
              <span class="history-group-label">Education</span>
            </div>
            <div class="history-list">

              <div class="history-item">
                <div class="history-meta">
                  <span class="history-role">Homeschool Graduate</span>
                  <span class="history-date">2001 – Jun 2013</span>
                </div>
                <div class="history-place">Cowperthwaite Academy &mdash; Thomaston, ME</div>
              </div>

              <div class="history-item">
                <div class="history-meta">
                  <span class="history-role">Culinary Arts</span>
                  <span class="history-date">Dec 2015 – Jan 2016</span>
                </div>
                <div class="history-place">Auguste Escoffier School &mdash; Austin, TX</div>
                <div class="history-note">Left after 5 weeks — real kitchens teach faster</div>
              </div>

            </div>
          </div>

        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <div class="divider-animated"></div>

    <!-- ===== WHERE I'VE BEEN ===== -->
    <section class="section section-blue-tint">
      <h2 class="section-heading reveal">Where I've Been</h2>
      <p class="section-sub reveal">Maine-rooted, with a Texas chapter in the middle.</p>

      <div class="places-track stagger">
        <div class="place-chip reveal">
          <span class="place-dot place-dot-blue"></span>
          <span class="place-name">Rockland, ME</span>
        </div>
        <svg class="place-arrow" width="16" height="16" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" aria-hidden="true"><polyline points="9 18 15 12 9 6"/></svg>
        <div class="place-chip reveal">
          <span class="place-dot place-dot-blue"></span>
          <span class="place-name">Camden / Rockport, ME</span>
        </div>
        <svg class="place-arrow" width="16" height="16" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" aria-hidden="true"><polyline points="9 18 15 12 9 6"/></svg>
        <div class="place-chip reveal">
          <span class="place-dot place-dot-ember"></span>
          <span class="place-name">Austin, TX</span>
        </div>
        <svg class="place-arrow" width="16" height="16" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" aria-hidden="true"><polyline points="9 18 15 12 9 6"/></svg>
        <div class="place-chip reveal">
          <span class="place-dot place-dot-ember"></span>
          <span class="place-name">Fort Worth, TX</span>
        </div>
        <svg class="place-arrow" width="16" height="16" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" aria-hidden="true"><polyline points="9 18 15 12 9 6"/></svg>
        <div class="place-chip reveal">
          <span class="place-dot place-dot-blue"></span>
          <span class="place-name">Thomaston / Palermo, ME</span>
        </div>
        <svg class="place-arrow" width="16" height="16" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" aria-hidden="true"><polyline points="9 18 15 12 9 6"/></svg>
        <div class="place-chip place-chip-current reveal">
          <span class="place-dot place-dot-blue"></span>
          <span class="place-name">Bangor, ME</span>
          <span class="place-now">now</span>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <div class="divider-animated"></div>

    <!-- ===== CONTACT ===== -->
    <section class="section section-blue-tint">
      <h2 class="section-heading reveal">Say Hi</h2>
      <p class="section-sub reveal">
        Not hiring, not for hire. But if something here caught your attention &mdash; I'm around.
      </p>

      <div class="contact-grid stagger">

        <a
          href="mailto:shadowwalkernc@gmail.com"
          class="contact-card card card-glow-blue reveal"
          aria-label="Send an email to Nate"
        >
          <div class="contact-card-icon" aria-hidden="true">
            <svg width="32" height="32" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.8" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><rect x="2" y="4" width="20" height="16" rx="2"/><path d="m2 7 10 7 10-7"/></svg>
          </div>
          <div class="contact-card-body">
            <div class="contact-card-label">Email</div>
            <div class="contact-card-value">shadowwalkernc@gmail.com</div>
            <p class="contact-card-note">
              Best for anything worth an actual conversation &mdash; feedback, ideas, a weird
              collaboration, or just wanting to talk shop about kitchen tech. I respond within a couple of days.
            </p>
          </div>
          <div class="contact-card-cta">Send a message &rarr;</div>
        </a>

        <a
          href="https://github.com/ShadowWalkerNC"
          target="_blank"
          rel="noopener noreferrer"
          class="contact-card card card-glow-blue reveal"
          aria-label="View Nate's GitHub profile"
        >
          <div class="contact-card-icon" aria-hidden="true">
            <svg width="32" height="32" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.8" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="M9 19c-5 1.5-5-2.5-7-3m14 6v-3.87a3.37 3.37 0 0 0-.94-2.61c3.14-.35 6.44-1.54 6.44-7A5.44 5.44 0 0 0 20 4.77 5.07 5.07 0 0 0 19.91 1S18.73.65 16 2.48a13.38 13.38 0 0 0-7 0C6.27.65 5.09 1 5.09 1A5.07 5.07 0 0 0 5 4.77a5.44 5.44 0 0 0-1.5 3.78c0 5.42 3.3 6.61 6.44 7A3.37 3.37 0 0 0 9 18.13V22"/></svg>
          </div>
          <div class="contact-card-body">
            <div class="contact-card-label">GitHub</div>
            <div class="contact-card-value">ShadowWalkerNC</div>
            <p class="contact-card-note">
              Everything I'm actively building lives here. Open an issue, leave feedback,
              or dig through the repos. Pull requests on anything public are genuinely welcome.
            </p>
          </div>
          <div class="contact-card-cta">View profile &rarr;</div>
        </a>

      </div>
    </section>

  </main>
</BaseLayout>

<style>
.section-blue-tint {
  background: linear-gradient(180deg, rgba(37,99,235,0.04) 0%, transparent 100%);
  border-top: 1px solid rgba(37,99,235,0.12);
}
.section-blue-wash {
  background: linear-gradient(180deg, rgba(37,99,235,0.06) 0%, rgba(99,102,241,0.03) 100%);
  border-top: 1px solid rgba(37,99,235,0.10);
  border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(37,99,235,0.10);
}
.about-hero {
  position: relative;
  padding: 5rem 1.5rem 4rem;
  overflow: hidden;
  border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(37,99,235,0.18);
}
.about-hero::after {
  content: '';
  position: absolute; inset: 0;
  background: linear-gradient(135deg, rgba(37,99,235,0.07) 0%, transparent 60%);
  pointer-events: none;
}
.about-hero-inner {
  position: relative; z-index: 2;
  max-width: 680px; margin: 0 auto;
  text-align: center;
  display: flex; flex-direction: column; align-items: center; gap: 0;
}
.about-hero-inner .badge { margin-bottom: 1.25rem; display: inline-flex; align-items: center; gap: 0.35rem; }
.about-hero-title {
  font-size: clamp(2rem, 5vw, 3.2rem);
  font-weight: 900; letter-spacing: -0.03em; line-height: 1.1;
  color: var(--text-primary); margin-bottom: 1.25rem;
}
.about-hero-sub {
  font-size: 1rem; color: var(--text-muted);
  line-height: 1.75; max-width: 560px; margin-bottom: 1.25rem;
}
.about-hero-back { font-size: 0.88rem; }

/* shimmer text */
.shimmer-text {
  background: linear-gradient(90deg, var(--accent-blue), var(--accent-indigo), var(--accent-blue));
  background-size: 200% auto;
  -webkit-background-clip: text;
  -webkit-text-fill-color: transparent;
  background-clip: text;
  animation: shimmer 3s linear infinite;
}

/* Who I Am */
.who-grid {
  display: grid;
  grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fill, minmax(280px, 1fr));
  gap: 1.25rem;
}
.who-card { display: flex; flex-direction: column; gap: 0.6rem; padding: 1.75rem 1.5rem; }
.card-blue-left {
  border-left: 3px solid rgba(37,99,235,0.30);
  background: linear-gradient(135deg, rgba(37,99,235,0.05) 0%, var(--bg-elevated) 60%);
}
.card-blue-left:hover { border-left-color: var(--accent-blue); }
.who-card-icon { color: var(--accent-blue); opacity: 0.75; line-height: 1; display: flex; align-items: center; }
.who-card-title { font-size: 1.05rem; font-weight: 700; color: var(--text-primary); margin: 0; }
.who-card-text { font-size: 0.88rem; color: var(--text-muted); line-height: 1.65; margin: 0; }

/* Work History */
.history-cols {
  display: grid;
  grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
  gap: 2rem;
  align-items: start;
}
.history-right {
  display: flex;
  flex-direction: column;
}
.history-group {
  display: flex;
  flex-direction: column;
  gap: 0.6rem;
}
.history-group-header {
  display: flex;
  align-items: center;
  gap: 0.5rem;
  margin-bottom: 0.25rem;
}
.history-icon {
  display: inline-flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center;
  width: 26px; height: 26px;
  background: var(--accent-blue-pale);
  color: var(--accent-blue);
  border-radius: var(--radius-md);
  flex-shrink: 0;
  border: 1px solid rgba(37,99,235,0.15);
}
.history-group-label {
  font-size: 0.68rem;
  font-weight: 800;
  text-transform: uppercase;
  letter-spacing: 0.12em;
  color: var(--accent-blue);
}
.history-list {
  display: flex;
  flex-direction: column;
  gap: 0;
  border-left: 2px solid rgba(37,99,235,0.15);
  padding-left: 1rem;
}
.history-item {
  padding: 0.65rem 0;
  border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border-subtle);
}
.history-item:last-child { border-bottom: none; }
.history-item-highlight .history-place { color: var(--accent-blue); }
.history-meta {
  display: flex;
  justify-content: space-between;
  align-items: baseline;
  gap: 0.5rem;
  flex-wrap: wrap;
}
.history-role {
  font-size: 0.88rem;
  font-weight: 700;
  color: var(--text-primary);
}
.history-date {
  font-size: 0.72rem;
  font-weight: 600;
  color: var(--text-muted);
  white-space: nowrap;
}
.history-place {
  font-size: 0.82rem;
  color: var(--text-secondary);
  margin-top: 0.1rem;
}
.history-note {
  font-size: 0.75rem;
